# **AX-Power 4 Plus**

Power supply unit with PoE switch, possibility for reserve power and smart solutions for expansion and installation. ![](images/_page_0_Picture_5.jpeg)

### Introduction

AX-Power 4 is a power supply unit PoE (Power over Ethernet) according to the standard IEEE 802.3at, with the possibility of uninterruptible power as the unit has room for 4 pcs. batteries (12V 7.2-9 Ah).
